Name: MEMORY CORE
checklistText:
<size=22>OBC MEMORY CORE LIST</size>

#$01: Time of Ignition (Tx) hours/minutes (HHHMM)
#$02: Time of Ignition (Tx) seconds/ms (0SSss)
#$08: Ascent: Yaw guidance (0 off, 1 on)
#$09: Ascent Azimuth. Will automatically calc roll 
		program and sets #$10, #$11  (XXX.XX)
#$10: Ascent guidance: Set target inclination (if not using #$09)
#$11: Roll Program: delta roll (if not using #$09)
#$12: Separation Velocity
#$19: Time to Retrograde (MMMSS)
#$25: IVI dV x (XXXX.X)
#$26: IVI dV y (XXXX.X)
#$27: IVI dV z (XXXX.X)
#$32: Current Orbit Plane Azimuth (Inclination) (XXX.XX)
#$33: Target Orbit Plane Azimuth (Inclination) (XXX.XX)
#$52: dV at Ap to modify Pe for target orbit
#$56: Set target orbit perigee (reference only)
#$57: Set target orbit apogee (reference only)
#$72: Total IV (XXXXX ft/s)
#$73: Computed Time from Lift-Off to Apogee (TAP)
#$74: Time to next apogee or perigee, whichever comes first (sec)
#$75: Time to Ap (sec)
#$76: Time to Pe (sec)
#$77: Orbit Period
#$78: Seconds since Pe
#$80: dV (X-Body)  (XXXX.X)
#$81: dV (Y-Body)  (XXXX.X)
#$82: dV (Z-Body)  (XXXX.X)
#$83: Orbital Angle to Go to Rendezvous (XXX.XX deg)
#$84: Time to Ignition (T minus Tx, minutes/seconds) (MMMSS)
#$90: RTOGO
#$98: Current Apogee (XXXX.X)
#$99: Current Perigee (XXXX.X)
